PrecisAmendment to Minute in Council P.C. 2018-834 of June 21, 2018, by replacing “Trial Division of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador” with “Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador” and “Court of Appeal of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador” with “Court of Appeal of Newfoundland and Labrador”.
